data.value: Yahtzee is a classic game that's been entertaining families since 1956. The ultimate goal of the game is to score major points by rolling a Yahtzee (five-of-a-kind), but if that doesn't happen, you can also score by rolling a three or a four-of-a-kind, or a full house! Yahtzee is a game of luck and strategy that will keep players rolling for more.
